## IEmbeddable.reload() method

Reload the embeddable so output and rendering is up to date. Especially relevant if the embeddable takes relative time as input (e.g. now to now-15)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
reload(): void;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`void`
